metadata.name: Mid'Birds - Edition
metadata.description:
Mid'Birds are a derivative of Moonbirds created with AI. "Mid" is a reference point in your learning, development, or building path. "Birds" vibe with and lift others on their journey. 

Holders of Mid'Birds - Edition are able to redeem a made-to-order 1 of 1 AI art piece from the artist. And there may or may not be cool updates to the Mid'Birbs - Edition piece.
